I've been making this for years, and it's wonderful. I usually use uncured bacon instead of pancetta. IMPORTANT: If your sauce is coming out watery, it's because you didn't allow it to reduce for long enough. It is not a problem with the recipe itself, and it's easy to fix. The cooking time in the recipe is way off. Go by the look and feel of the sauce, not your kitchen timer, and you will be very happy with this recipe.

